# what types of apis for endpoints exist? i know of anthropic and openai, but what else do i miss?

to each of the apis: what are their endpoints? provide a brief table

Several major LLM API providers offer endpoints beyond OpenAI and Anthropic, including Google Gemini, Cohere, Mistral AI, and Groq, which are popular for inference, embeddings, and chat in 2026. These APIs typically follow OpenAI-compatible patterns like /chat/completions for chat or /embeddings for vectors, but each has unique ones too.[^1_1][^1_2][^1_3][^1_4]

## OpenAI Endpoints

OpenAI's API focuses on versatile generation and processing.[^1_5][^1_6]


| Endpoint | Purpose |
| :-- | :-- |
| POST /v1/chat/completions | Chat conversations with models like GPT.[^1_5] |
| POST /v1/completions | Legacy text completion.[^1_5] |
| POST /v1/embeddings | Text embeddings.[^1_5] |
| GET /v1/models | List available models.[^1_5] |

## Anthropic Endpoints

Anthropic (Claude) emphasizes safe, structured messaging.[^1_4][^1_7]


| Endpoint | Purpose |
| :-- | :-- |
| POST /v1/messages | Primary chat messaging.[^1_4] |
| POST /chat/completions | OpenAI-compatible chat.[^1_4] |

## Google Gemini Endpoints

Gemini uses Google's generative API for multimodal tasks.[^1_8][^1_9]


| Endpoint | Purpose |
| :-- | :-- |
| POST /v1beta/models/{model}:generateContent | Content generation (chat/images).[^1_8] |
| POST /v1beta/models/{model}:countTokens | Token counting.[^1_8] |

## Cohere Endpoints

Cohere specializes in classification and reranking alongside chat.[^1_10][^1_11]


| Endpoint | Purpose |
| :-- | :-- |
| POST /v1/chat | Conversational chat.[^1_10] |
| POST /v1/classify | Text classification.[^1_10] |
| POST /v1/rerank | Search reranking.[^1_11] |

## Mistral AI Endpoints

Mistral offers OpenAI-style endpoints for their open-weight models.[^1_12][^1_13]


| Endpoint | Purpose |
| :-- | :-- |
| POST /v1/chat/completions | Chat completions.[^1_12] |
| GET /v1/models | List models.[^1_12] |
| POST /v1/fim/completions | Fill-in-middle for code.[^1_13] |

## Groq Endpoints

Groq provides ultra-fast inference with OpenAI compatibility.[^1_14]


| Endpoint | Purpose |
| :-- | :-- |
| POST /openai/v1/chat/completions | High-speed chat (OpenAI format).[^1_14] |
| POST /v1/chat/completions | Native fast chat.[^1_14] |

